se}} 0.8%\n| prevseason         = [[1972 1. divisjon|1972]]\n| nextseason         = [[1974 1. divisjon|1974]]\n}}\nThe '''1973 [[Eliteserien|1. divisjon]]''' was the 28th completed season of top division [[association football|football]] in [[Norway]].\n\n==Overview==\nIt was contested by 12 teams, and [[Viking FK]] won the championship, their second consecutive league title and their third top-flight title overall.\n\nFredrikstad, who was the only remaining team to have played all 28 completed seasons in the top division, was relegated in the end of the season.\n\n==Teams and locations==\n:''Note: Table lists in alphabetical order.\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" border=\"1\"\n|-\n! Team\n!{{Tooltip| Ap. | Appearances in top divisions of Norwegian football}}<!--Begins with 1937\u201338 season. Abandoned 1939\u201340 season does not count.-->\n! Location\n! Stadium\n|-\n| [[SK Brann|Brann]]\n| align=\"center\"| '''21'''\n| [[Bergen]]\n| [[Brann Stadion]]\n|-\n| [[Fredrikstad FK|Fredrikstad]]\n| align=\"center\"| '''28'''\n| [[Fredrikstad]]\n| [[Old Fredrikstad Stadion|Fredrikstad Stadion]]\n|-\n| [[Frigg Oslo FK|Frigg]]\n| align=\"center\"| '''15'''\n| [[Oslo]]\n| \n|-\n| [[HamKam]]\n| align=\"center\"| '''5'''\n| [[Hamar]]\n| [[Briskeby Arena|Briskeby]]\n|-\n| [[Lyn Fotball|Lyn]]\n| align=\"center\"| '''20'''\n| [[Oslo]]\n| [[Ullevaal Stadion]]\n|-\n| [[Mj\u00f8ndalen IF|Mj\u00f8ndalen]]\n| align=\"center\"| '''7'''\n| [[Mj\u00f8ndalen]]\n| [[Nedre Eiker Stadion]]\n|-\n| [[Raufoss Fotball|Raufoss]]\n| align=\"center\"| '''8'''\n| [[Raufoss]]\n| Raufoss Stadion\n|-\n| [[Rosenborg BK|Rosenborg]]\n| align=\"center\"| '''11'''\n| [[Trondheim]]\n| [[Lerkendal Stadion]]\n|-\n| [[Skeid Fotball|Skeid]]\n| align=\"center\"| '''26'''\n| [[Oslo]]\n| \n|-\n| [[IK Start|Start]]\n| align=\"center\"| '''6'''\n| [[Kristiansand]]\n| [[Kristiansand Stadion]]\n|-\n| [[Str\u00f8msgodset Toppfotball|Str\u00f8msgodset]]\n| align=\"center\"| '''8'''\n| [[Drammen]]\n| [[Marienlyst Stadion]]\n|-\n| [[Viking FK|Viking]]\n| align=\"center\"| '''26'''\n| [[Stavanger]]\n| [[Stavanger Stadion]]\n|}\n\n==League table==\n<onlyinclude>{{#invoke:sports table|main|style=WDL\n|res_col_header=QR\n|winpoints=2\n\n|team1=VIK|name_VIK=[[Viking FK|Viking]]\n|team2=ROS|name_ROS=[[Rosenborg BK|Rosenborg]]\n|team3=IKS|name_IKS=[[IK Start|Start]]\n|team4=HAM|name_HAM=[[HamKam]]\n|team5=BRA|name_BRA=[[SK Brann|Brann]]\n|team6=STR|name_STR=[[Str\u00f8msgodset IF|Str\u00f8msgodset]]\n|team7=SKD|name_SKD=[[Skeid Fotball|Skeid]]\n|team8=RAU|name_RAU=[[Raufoss IL|Raufoss]]\n|team9=MIF|name_MIF=[[Mj\u00f8ndalen IF|Mj\u00f8ndalen]]\n|team10=FRI|name_FRI=[[Frigg Oslo FK|Frigg]]\n|team11=LYN|name_LYN=[[FK Lyn|Lyn]]\n|team12=FFK|name_FFK=[[Fredrikstad FK|Fredrikstad]]\n\n|win_VIK=13|draw_VIK=6|loss_VIK=3|gf_VIK=30|ga_VIK=13|status_VIK=C\n|win_ROS=10|draw_ROS=7|loss_ROS=5|gf_ROS=32|ga_ROS=18\n|win_IKS=10|draw_IKS=6|loss_IKS=6|gf_IKS=28|ga_IKS=22\n|win_HAM=9|draw_HAM=7|loss_HAM=6|gf_HAM=29|ga_HAM=25\n|win_BRA=9|draw_BRA=5|loss_BRA=8|gf_BRA=31|ga_BRA=27\n|win_STR=9|draw_STR=4|loss_STR=9|gf_STR=30|ga_STR=27\n|win_SKD=8|draw_SKD=6|loss_SKD=8|gf_SKD=20|ga_SKD=21\n|win_RAU=7|draw_RAU=7|loss_RAU=8|gf_RAU=21|ga_RAU=26\n|win_MIF=7|draw_MIF=7|loss_MIF=8|gf_MIF=21|ga_MIF=26\n|win_FRI=5|draw_FRI=8|loss_FRI=9|gf_FRI=21|ga_FRI=27|status_FRI=R\n|win_LYN=5|draw_LYN=6|loss_LYN=11|gf_LYN=23|ga_LYN=31|status_LYN=R\n|win_FFK=3|draw_FFK=5|loss_FFK=14|gf_FFK=20|ga_FFK=43|status_FFK=R\n\n|col_EC1=green1|text_EC1=Qualification for the [[1974\u201375 European Cup|European Cup first round]]\n|result1=EC1\n|col_UC1=blue1|text_UC1=Qualification for the [[1974\u201375 UEFA Cup|UEFA Cup first round]]\n|result2=UC1|result3=UC1\n|col_ECWC1=#FFEBAD|text_ECWC1=Qualification for the [[1974\u201375 European Cup Winners' Cup|Cup Winners' Cup first round]]\n|result6=ECWC1\n|col_R=red1|text_R=Relegation to [[1974 2. divisjon|2. divisjon]]\n|result10=R|result11=R|result12=R\n\n|update=complete\n|class_rules=1) points;